Traineeship &nbsp;&nbsp;Description:
This position reports to the Senior Valuer and interfaces with company managers and HR staff. GSK Global Pte Ltd is committed to an employee-orientated, high performance culture that emphasises empowerment, quality, continuous improvement, and the recruitment and on-going development of a superior workplace.

Trainee to be involved in:
- Conduct site inspections
- Analyze and document findings
- Communicate and summarise results
- Prepare valuation reports
- Coordinating with various government bodies, private businesses or individuals on the preparation of quotation and reports
- Leadership and Management
- Other ad-hoc assigned